List all indexes:
     | eventcount summarize=false index=* index=_* | dedup index | fields index

Firewall log query for portscanners (CIM compliant)
     earliest=-1h index=<firewall index> sourcetype=<firewall>
     | fields src, dest_port
     | where (NOT cidrmatch("10.0.0.0/8",src) AND NOT cidrmatch("192.168.0.0/16",src) AND NOT cidrmatch("172.16.0.0/20",src))
     | stats dc(dest_port) as "Port Count" by src
     | iplocation src
     | sort - "Port Count"
     | head 10
     | table src, City, Country, "Port Count"
